  Hand to newly-born proaudio herd.

*sweep-0.9.2 (13 Feb 2007)

  13 Feb 2007; Alexis Ballier <aballier@gentoo.org> +sweep-0.9.2.ebuild:
  Version bump, closing bug #166409

  05 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Convert to use elog.

  14 Dec 2006; Christian Birchinger <joker@gentoo.org>
  -sweep-0.8.2-r1.ebuild, sweep-0.8.3.ebuild, sweep-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Removed unneeded dev-libs/tdb dependency. Cleaned old 0.8.2-r1 version.

*sweep-0.9.1 (08 Jul 2006)

  08 Jul 2006; Frank van de Pol <fvdpol@gentoo.org> +sweep-0.9.1.ebuild:
  Version bump to 0.9.1.

  26 Dec 2005; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.2-r1.ebuild,
  sweep-0.8.3.ebuild:
  oggvorbis Cleanup

  09 Dec 2005; <chainsaw@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.2-r1.ebuild,
  sweep-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Depend explicitly on GTK+ version 1.2 as version 2 does not work; closes bug #114403.

  15 Sep 2005; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Mark 0.8.3 stable on alpha

  26 Aug 2005; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc

  04 Jun 2005; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

  28 May 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.2-r1.ebuild,
  sweep-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Dont make use of the deprecated oggvorbis useflag any longer, see #94254.
  Marked 0.8.3 stable on amd64 and x86.

  05 May 2005; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.2-r1.ebuild,
  sweep-0.8.3.ebuild:
  Removed * postfix from <, <=, >= and > dependencies.

  01 May 2005; Michael Hanselmann <hansmi@gentoo.org> sweep-0.8.2-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on ppc.

